                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le bel instituteur de filles\nQue ce monsieur De Fénelon !\nIl parle de messe et d'aiguilles :\nMaman, c'est un sot tout du long.\nConcerts, bals et pièces nouvelles\nNous instruisent mieux que cela.\nTra la la la, les demoiselles,\nTra la la la, se forment là."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Qu'à broder une autre s'applique ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Maman, je veux au piano,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Avec mon maître de musique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "D'Armide chanter le duo.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Je crois sentir les étincelles",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "De l'amour dont Renaud brûla.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, les demoiselles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, se forment là.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'à broder une autre s'applique ;\nMaman, je veux au piano,\nAvec mon maître de musique,\nD'Armide chanter le duo.\nJe crois sentir les étincelles\nDe l'amour dont Renaud brûla.\nTra la la la, les demoiselles,\nTra la la la, se forment là."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Qu'une autre écrive la dépense ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Maman, pendant une heure ou deux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Je veux que mon maître de danse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "M'enseigne un pas voluptueux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ma robe rend mes pieds rebelles :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Un peu plus haut relevons-la.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, les demoiselles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, se forment là.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qu'une autre écrive la dépense ;\nMaman, pendant une heure ou deux,\nJe veux que mon maître de danse\nM'enseigne un pas voluptueux.\nMa robe rend mes pieds rebelles :\nUn peu plus haut relevons-la.\nTra la la la, les demoiselles,\nTra la la la, se forment là."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Que sur ma sœur une autre veille ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Maman, je veux mettre au salon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Déja je dessine à merveille",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Les contours de cet Apollon.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Grand dieu, que ses formes sont belles !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Sur-tout les beaux nus que voilà !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, les demoiselles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, se forment là.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Que sur ma sœur une autre veille ;\nMaman, je veux mettre au salon.\nDéja je dessine à merveille\nLes contours de cet Apollon.\nGrand dieu, que ses formes sont belles !\nSur-tout les beaux nus que voilà !\nTra la la la, les demoiselles,\nTra la la la, se forment là."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Maman, il faut qu'on me marie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "La coutume ainsi l'exigeant.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Je t'avoûrai, ma chère amie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Que même le cas est urgent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Le monde sait de mes nouvelles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Mais on y rit de tout cela.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, les demoiselles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Tra la la la, se forment là.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Maman, il faut qu'on me marie,\nLa coutume ainsi l'exigeant.\nJe t'avoûrai, ma chère amie,\nQue même le cas est urgent.\nLe monde sait de mes nouvelles,\nMais on y rit de tout cela.\nTra la la la, les demoiselles,\nTra la la la, se forment là."
        }
    ],
